014715
- 1 -

(d) All recordings generated pursuant to this section are confidential pursuant to
§ 37-5-107.
(e) By December 1, 2027, the department must submit a report to the senate
judiciary committee and the committee of the house of representatives with jurisdiction
over subject matters pertaining to children on the results of the pilot program, including
recommendations on how to improve the pilot program.
SECTION 2. This act takes effect July 1, 2026, the public welfare requiring it.
